column2: "Are you doing well? You look like it. Lisa has been tired lately."
"Darkers are really troublesome. I want to kill them, but there are just too many."
"I want take my time to kill them all, but lately it's just been troublesome."
"Lisa likes to kill them but hates being attacked by them. It should be a one way relationship."
"That's why it would be nice for Darkers to die much quicker when Lisa shoots them."
"There are a lot of things I hate, but Darkers are what I hate the most. More than humans."
"Fufu, don't worry Lisa tends to like you more than not."
